{"tid":2183450,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［樣衰入］試過因為樣衰而最唔開心係咩事？","createTime":"2020-09-01T02:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T06:08:30.000Z","uid":343520,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"308e63bc7bc5fe60fc9a192df8146fe3142b813b","tid":2183450,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:54:56.000Z","msg":"每次追女仔都會失敗收場，而我追過既女仔一兩個月後一定會有拖拍，我只配做過客，幫手旺人地桃花運<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平凡像我路過 十個似我 情敵實在太多 <br />\n天都不理我 令我想清楚 <br />\n感情是來自由弱者所寫的悲歌 <br />\n事實上為什麼不拍到拖 說穿了我不美<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641a5e6d2510aab4fad1d8046eada6d38e50480d","tid":2183450,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1480f839ff153e287061dc2ea4a97007281d06e","tid":2183450,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"641a5e6d2510aab4fad1d8046eada6d38e50480d","tid":2183450,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:57:32.000Z","msg":"Sis樣衰？"},{"pid":"dc90bf06873b94ea7bddcb1d9bbd07a2ef2fedf1","tid":2183450,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T02:58:12.000Z","msg":"流水很清楚惜花這個責任 真的身份不過送運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},